#: ../../platforms.md:1
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "依赖"

#: ../../platforms.md:3
msgid "Node.js"
msgstr "Node.js"

#: ../../platforms.md:5
msgid ""
"Koffi requires a recent [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) version with "
"[N-API](https://nodejs.org/api/n-api.html) version 8 support:"
msgstr ""
"Koffi需要较新版本的[Node.js](https://nodejs.org/)，支持[N-API](https://nodejs.org/api/n-api.html)版本8:"

#: ../../platforms.md:7
msgid "Node < 12.22.0 is not supported"
msgstr "Node < 12.22.0不支持"

#: ../../platforms.md:8
msgid "_Node 12.x_: Node 12.22.0 or newer"
msgstr "_Node 12.x_: Node 12.22.0及以后"

#: ../../platforms.md:9
msgid "_Node 14.x_: Node 14.17.0 or newer"
msgstr "_Node 14.x_: Node 14.17.0及以后"

#: ../../platforms.md:10
msgid "_Node 15.x_: Node 15.12.0 or newer"
msgstr "_Node 15.x_: Node 15.12.0及以后"

#: ../../platforms.md:11
msgid "Node 16.0.0 or later versions"
msgstr "Node 16.0.0及之后的版本"

#: ../../platforms.md:13
msgid ""
"Use [NVM](https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm) to install more recent Node "
"versions on older Linux distributions."
msgstr ""
"使用[NVM](https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm)来在老的Linux发行版中安装更新的Node版本."

#: ../../platforms.md:15
msgid "Supported platforms"
msgstr "支持的平台"

#: ../../platforms.md:17
msgid ""
"The following combinations of OS and architectures __are officially "
"supported and tested__ at the moment:"
msgstr ""
"下列系统和架构的组合当前__被官方支持并测试过__:"

#: ../../platforms.md
msgid "ISA / OS"
msgstr "架构 \\ 系统"

#: ../../platforms.md
msgid "Windows"
msgstr "Windows"

#: ../../platforms.md
msgid "Linux"
msgstr "Linux"

#: ../../platforms.md
msgid "macOS"
msgstr "macOS"

#: ../../platforms.md
msgid "FreeBSD"
msgstr "FreeBSD"

#: ../../platforms.md
msgid "OpenBSD"
msgstr "OpenBSD"

#: ../../platforms.md
msgid "x86 (IA32) [^1]"
msgstr "x86 (IA32) [^1]"

#: ../../platforms.md
msgid "✅ Yes"
msgstr "✅ Yes"

#: ../../platforms.md
msgid "⬜️ *N/A*"
msgstr "⬜️ *N/A*"

#: ../../platforms.md
msgid "x86_64 (AMD64)"
msgstr "x86_64 (AMD64)"

#: ../../platforms.md
