#: ../../platforms.md:31
msgid ""
"For all fully supported platforms (green check marks), a prebuilt binary "
"is included in the NPM package which means you can install Koffi without "
"a C++ compiler."
msgstr ""
"对于所有完整支持的平台(绿色对勾标记), NPM包中包含了预编译的二进制, 因此你不需要一个C++编译器就能安装Koffi."

#: ../../platforms.md:27
msgid ""
"The following call conventions are supported for forward calls: cdecl, "
"stdcall, MS fastcall, thiscall. Only cdecl and stdcall can be used for C "
"to JS callbacks."
msgstr ""
"正向调用支持的调用协定: cdecl, stdcall, MS fastcall, thiscall. 从C向JS的回调仅可使用cdecl和stdcall."

#: ../../platforms.md:28
msgid ""
"The prebuilt binary uses the hard float ABI and expects a VFP "
"coprocessor. Build from source to use Koffi with a different ABI (softfp,"
" soft)."
msgstr ""
"预编译的二进制使用了hard float ABI, 需要VFP协处理器. 从代码构建来让Koffi使用一个其他ABI(softfp, soft)."

#: ../../platforms.md:29
msgid ""
"The prebuilt binary uses the LP64D (double-precision float) ABI. The LP64"
" ABI is supported in theory if you build Koffi from source (untested), "
"the LP64F ABI is not supported."
msgstr ""
"预编译的二进制使用了LP64D(双精度浮点)ABI. 通过从源代码编译Koffi理论上支持LP64 ABI(未测试), 不支持LP64F ABI."
